The Golden Thread

The strongest version isn’t:

“We are destined.”

It’s:

“We can repeatedly discover, compress, and deploy useful patterns.”

That claim can be tested.

And if it keeps working, people will eventually notice without needing to be convinced.

Vision captures the possibility.

Execution captures the territory.